@startuml client_creation_nonblocking
title Client Application Creation - Non-Blocking with Callback Notification

actor "Client Application" as Client
participant "PersistencyFactory" as PFactory
participant "ConfigProviderFactory" as CPFactory
participant "ConfigProviderImpl" as CPImpl
participant "ProxyThread" as ProxyThread
' participant "ProxyFuture" as ProxyFuture
' participant "ServiceDiscovery" as SD

== Step 1: Create Persistency ==

Client -> PFactory: Create(kvs_handle)
PFactory -> PFactory: new PersistencyImpl(kvs_handle)
PFactory --> Client: unique_ptr<Persistency>

== Step 2: Create ConfigProvider (Non-Blocking Mode) ==

note over Client: Non-blocking approach:\nRegister callback for connection notification

Client -> CPFactory: Create(persistency,\n  wait_timeout=0ms,\n  callback=[&](){ onProxyReady(); })
CPFactory -> CPFactory: Create ProxyFuture for InternalConfigProvider
CPFactory -> CPImpl: new ConfigProviderImpl(\n  proxy_future,\n  persistency,\n  callback)

note over CPImpl: Constructor starts
CPImpl -> CPImpl: ReadCachedParameterSets from Persistency
note over CPImpl: Cache populated with kUnqualified parameter sets

CPImpl -> ProxyThread: Start proxy_available_thread_\nwith callback
activate ProxyThread
note over ProxyThread: Background thread waiting for proxy

CPImpl --> CPFactory: ConfigProvider instance
CPFactory --> Client: unique_ptr<ConfigProvider>

note over Client: Constructor returns immediately\n(non-blocking)

== Step 3: Continue with Other Initialization ==

Client -> Client: Initialize other components
Client -> Client: Perform other startup tasks
note over Client: Application continues without blocking

== Step 4: Early Access to Cached Data ==

note over Client: ConfigProvider already usable\nwith cached data from Persistency

Client -> CPImpl: GetParameterSet("CachedConfig")
alt In cache (from Persistency)
    note over CPImpl: Cache hit - serve immediately
    CPImpl --> Client: shared_ptr<ParameterSet> (kUnqualified)
else Not in cache
    note over CPImpl: Proxy not ready yet
    CPImpl --> Client: Error: kProxyNotReady
end

== Step 5: Proxy Connection (Background) ==

par Background Proxy Discovery
    ' ProxyThread -> ProxyFuture: Get(stop_token)
    ' ProxyFuture -> SD: Find InternalConfigProvider proxy
    ' SD -> SD: Search for ConfigDaemon service
    note over ProxyThread: Service discovery process
    ' SD --> ProxyFuture: Proxy found
    ' ProxyFuture --> ProxyThread: unique_ptr<InternalConfigProvider>

    ProxyThread -> CPImpl: SetupInternalConfigProvider(proxy, callback)

    note over CPImpl: Initial synchronization
    ' CPImpl -> CPImpl: TrySubscribeToLastUpdatedParameterSetEvent()
    ' CPImpl -> CPImpl: FetchInitialParameterSetValuesFrom()
    ' CPImpl -> CPImpl: WriteInitialParameterSetValuesToPersistentCache()
    ' CPImpl -> CPImpl: CacheInitialQualifierState()
    ' CPImpl -> CPImpl: RegisterCallbacksForPersistedParameterSetNames()
    ' CPImpl -> CPImpl: StartParameterSetUpdatePollingRoutine()

    CPImpl -> Client: callback: onProxyReady()
    note over Client: Async notification received\nProxy is now connected

    ' CPImpl -> CPImpl: Notify internal_config_provider_cv_
end

deactivate ProxyThread

@enduml
